Text:
Hi Dale, 

This is Steve from Solar First based in Fort Myers. I am our company’s Co-Founder and serve as the Chief Innovation Officer. I also live in Cape Coral. 

I believe you provided your phone number with interest in Solar Energy Storage via a post of ours on Facebook.  I was provided your contact information as a result of that. 

I just tried calling. Your voicemail inbox was not set up so I could not leave a voicemail. 

I’m free today if Sunday is a good day for you. Or, please let me know a day/time you prefer and I can call then. Looking forward to learning how I can best serve
